      "title": "Face covering is mandatory in public places",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Director General of Health Services, Dr. Asela Gunawardena, said that in view of the current 'Covid-19' situation in the country, it was made mandatory to wear face masks in public places, domestic gatherings and public transport.",
        "The 'Covid-19' virus has been spreading in Sri Lanka for about a week."
      ],
